snippet.title: Equestrian the Game BETA gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Equestrian the Game beta is now available in select regions! Learn more at https://equestrianthegame.com/

Thank you all for following the development of Equestrian! We're super excited to take our first step towards fully releasing the game!

Follow us on Instagram for weekly updates @equestrianthegame 
TikTok: @equestrian_the_game
